{"article_id":"OULJHC8VWpPdfbeT","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Iran has again rejected suggestions","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that one of its missiles brought down a Ukrainian passenger jet near the capital , Tehran , on Wednesday .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Its civil aviation chief said on Friday","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"he was `` certain ''","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"that the plane was not hit by a missile .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"He was responding to claims by Western leaders","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"that evidence suggested","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"the plane had been hit by a surface-to-air missile , possibly in error .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"New video appeared to show a plane","depth":3},{"id":9,"text":"being hit by a projectile over Tehran .","depth":3},{"id":10,"text":"The crash of Ukraine International Airlines flight PS752 with the loss of 176 lives came","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"just hours after Iran carried out missile strikes on two airbases","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"housing US forces in Iraq .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"US media have speculated","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that the airliner may have been mistaken for a warplane","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"as Iran prepared for possible US retaliation .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Victims of the crash included 82 Iranians , 63 Canadians and 11 Ukrainians as well as nationals from Sweden , the UK , Afghanistan and Germany .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Iran has promised a full investigation .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"However , TV images from the crash site on Thursday showed a mechanical digger","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"helping to clear debris away ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"raising concerns","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that important evidence could have been removed .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Skip","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Twitter post by @ elizapalmer","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"CBS crew just visited the # Ukrainian airlines crash site west of Tehran .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Nine am local time .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Virtually all pieces of the plane were removed yesterday","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"-","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"say locals .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Scavengers now picking site clean .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"No security .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"Not cordoned off .","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"No sign of any investigators .","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"pic.twitter.com/hhNJyokhjq","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"- Elizabeth Palmer","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"( @ elizapalmer )","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"January 10 , 2020","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Report","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"Meanwhile , the so-called `` black box ''","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"recovered from the wreckage","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"will be opened on Friday ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Iran 's official Irna news agency reported .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Iran said","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"it would download the information itself ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that the process could take up to two months .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Black boxes contain the flight data recorder and the cockpit voice recorder ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"and could provide vital clues about what caused the crash .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"At a news conference on Friday , Iran 's Civil Aviation Organisation","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"( CAOI )","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"chief Ali Abedzadeh repeated his view","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"that a missile was not the cause of the crash .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"`` The thing","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"that is clear to us","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"and that we can say with certainty","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"is that this plane was not hit by a missile , ''","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"`` As I said last night ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"this plane for more than one and a half minutes was on fire","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"and was in the air ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"and the location shows","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"that the pilot was attempting to return . ''","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"On Thursday , government spokesman Ali Rabiei accused the US and its allies of `` lying","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"and engaging in psychological warfare '' in their speculation over the cause of the accident .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"An Iranian official told the BBC on Friday","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"that there was documentation","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"to prove","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"that the plane had a mechanical issue before take-off .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"It was not signed off for flying ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"but Ukrainian airline officials had overruled these objections ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"the official said ,","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"without giving further details .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau said","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"he had received intelligence from multiple sources","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"indicating","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"the plane was shot down by an Iranian surface-to-air missile ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"that it was possible that this was unintentional .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"`` This reinforces the need for a thorough investigation , ''","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"`` Canadians have questions","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"and they deserve answers . ''","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"But he said","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"it was too early to apportion blame","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"or draw any conclusions ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"and refused to go into detail about the evidence .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"The Ukrainian flight was headed to the Canadian city of Toronto via the Ukrainian capital , Kyiv .","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"UK Prime Minister Boris Johnson echoed Mr Trudeau 's words","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"Britain was working closely with Canada and other international partners","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"affected by the crash .","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"Speaking in Canada ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"UK Foreign Secretary Dominic Raab said","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"British nationals were advised not to travel to Iran ,","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"`` given the body of information","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"that UIA Flight 752 was shot down by an Iranian surface-to-air missile ,","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"and the heightened tensions '' .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"Newsweek quoted a Pentagon and senior US intelligence officials , as well as an Iraqi intelligence official ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"as saying","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"they believed","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"flight PS752 was hit by a Russian-made Tor missile .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Ukraine said on Friday","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"that the US had passed on `` important data '' about the crash to President 's Volodymyr Zelensky ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"without providing any further details .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"US Secretary of State Mike Pompeo later said","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"he spoke with Mr Zelensky","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"to express his `` deepest condolences for the lives","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"lost in the tragic crash '' .","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"Video","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"obtained by the New York Times","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"appeared to show a missile streaking across the night sky over Tehran","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"and then exploding on contact with a plane .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"About 10 seconds later , a loud explosion is heard on the ground .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"Iran initially said","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"it would not hand over the recovered `` black boxes '' to Boeing , the plane 's manufacturer , or to the US .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"This followed the killing of top Iranian general Qasem Soleimani in a US drone attack on 3 January and the subsequent strikes against US bases in Iraq on Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"However , the US National Transportation Safety Board","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"( NTSB )","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"later confirmed","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"it had been invited to take part in the investigation","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"and would send a representative .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Boeing said","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"it would support the NTSB in the inquiry ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"and the Transportation Safety Board of Canada said","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"it had also been invited to the accident site by Tehran .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"France 's BEA air accident agency said on Friday","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"it had also been invited to take part in the investigation .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":253,"left":136,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":134,"right":135,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":134,"left":131,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":128,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":2,"right":129,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":129,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":133,"left":5,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":135,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":173,"right":251,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{